---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<footer class="border-t border-gray-200 bg-gray-50 mt-auto">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-8">
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 text-center">
      &copy; {year} Victor Weeks &middot;
      Content: <a href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/" class="underline hover:text-gray-700">CC-BY-4.0</a> &middot;
      Code: <a href="https://opensource.org/licenses/MIT" class="underline hover:text-gray-700">MIT</a>
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 text-center mt-2">
      Supported by the <a href="https://bssw.io/fellowship" class="underline hover:text-gray-600">Better Scientific Software Fellowship Program</a>,
      funded by the U.S. Department of Energy and the National Science Foundation.
    </p>
  </div>
</footer>
